author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Banco Sabadell Q4 Net Profit at 147.7 Mln Euros
text:
Feb 2 (Reuters) - BANCO DE SABADELL SA:
* FY NET INTEREST INCOME 3.80 BILLION EUROS * Q4 NET INTEREST INCOME 924.6 MILLION EUROS * NON-PERFORMING LOANS RATIO 5.14 PERCENT AT END-DEC * FY NET PROFIT 801.5 MILLION EUROS * Q4 NET PROFIT 147.7 MILLION EUROS * RETURN ON TANGIBLE EQUITY (ROTE) 7.27 PERCENT AT END-DEC * COMMON EQUITY TIER 1 PHASE-IN 13.4 PERCENT AT END-DEC * COMMON EQUITY TIER 1 RATIO FULLY-LOADED 12.8 PERCENT AT END-DEC
* TO PRESENT STRATEGIC PLAN FOR 2018-2020 ON FEB. 23 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
